<h1>赏</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#009900;">shǎng</span><span class=alesi>(shang3)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 赏 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 赏</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/reward" style="color:black;">reward</a>, <a href="/dictionary/grant" style="color:black;">grant</a>, <a href="/dictionary/bestow" style="color:black;">bestow</a>; appreciate</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 12<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 12 strokes: <a href="/character/就" title="jiu4: just, simply; to come, go to; to approach, near">就</a>, <a href="/character/道" title="dao4: path, road, street; method, way">道</a>, <a href="/character/然" title="ran2: yes, certainly; pledge, promise">然</a>, <a href="/character/最" title="zui4: most, extremely, exceedingly">最</a>, <a href="/character/等" title="">等</a>, <a href="/character/斯" title="si1: this, thus, such; to lop off; emphatic particle">斯</a>, <a href="/character/提" title="ti2: hold in hand; lift in hand">提</a>, <a href="/character/量" title="liang4: measure, quantity, capacity">量</a>, <a href="/character/期" title="qi1: period of time; date; time limit">期</a>, <a href="/character/强" title="qiang2: strong, powerful, energetic">强</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/貝" title="Kangxi radical 154">貝</a>&nbsp;154.8</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 5 <br><small>Other HSK 5 characters: <a href="/character/骂" title="ma4: accuse, blame, curse, scold">骂</a>, <a href="/character/颗" title="ke1: grain, kernel">颗</a>, <a href="/character/贴" title="tie1: paste to, stick on; attached to">贴</a>, <a href="/character/幅" title="fu2: piece, strip, breadth of, hem">幅</a>, <a href="/character/腰" title="yao1: waist; kidney">腰</a>, <a href="/character/矛" title="mao2: spear, lance; KangXi radical 110">矛</a>, <a href="/character/眉" title="mei2: eyebrows; upper margin of book">眉</a>, <a href="/character/碍" title="ai4: obstruct, hinder, block, deter">碍</a>, <a href="/character/恋" title="lian4: love; long for, yearn for; love">恋</a>, <a href="/character/敏" title="min3: fast, quick, clever, smart">敏</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-5" title="List of HSK 5 characters"